title: Un Village Francais (A French Village) - season 7 (Eng subs)
description: Un Village Francais (A French Village) - season 7 This acclaimed drama is about the German occupation of France during World War II, and its effects on the inhabitants of a small village in Jura. In June 1940, the village of Villeneuve awakes to the arrival of the German army - and the next four years of occupation have a shattering effect on the lives of all its inhabitants. Softcoded English subtitles (Please select Track 1 on episodes 5 + 6, as track 2 is borked. For all other eps, there is just one track to choose from) Spoken language: French, and some German Not my rip, reencoded to a smaller size: 1280 x 720p, H.264, WEB-DL, MP4 Aired 2016 - 2017 12 x 46 - 64 minute episodes.
